quran[7{c,v,t}:
5,58,jab tum namaz ke liye munaadi karte ho to woh is ka mazaq uratay aur is se khailtay hain is ki wajah yeh hai ke woh aqal nahi rakhtay
5,59,"inn se kaho,"" ae ahal kitaab! tum jis baat par hum se bigre ho woh is ke siwa aur kya hai ke hum Allah par aur deen ki uss taleem par imaan le aeye hain jo hamari taraf nazil hui hai aur hum se pehlay bhi nazil hui thi, aur tum mein se aksar log fasik hain? """
5,60,"phir kaho"" kya mein unn logon ki nishandahi karoon jin ka anjaam khuda ke haan fasqoon ke anjaam se bhi badter hai? woh jin par khuda ne laanat ki, jin par uss ka ghazab toota, jin mein se bandar aur soor banaye gay, jinhon ne Taghoot ki bandagi ki un ka darja aur bhi ziyada bura hai aur woh sawa al-sabeelse bohat ziyada bhatkay hue hain """
5,61,"jab yeh tum logon ke paas atay hain to kehte hain ke hum imaan laaye, halaank kufar liye hue aeye thay aur kufar hi liye hue wapas gay aur Allah khoob jaanta hai jo kuch yeh dilon mein chupaye hue hain"
5,62,tum dekhte ho ke un mein se bakasrat log gunah aur zulm o zayad-ti ke kamon mein daud dhoop karte phirtay hain aur haraam ke maal khatay hain bohat buri harkaat hain jo yeh kar rahay hain
5,63,kyun inn ke u'lamaa٫ aur mashaiykh inhen gunah par zabaan kholnay aur haraam khanay se nahi roktay? yaqeenan bohat hi bura karnaama zindagi hai jo woh tayyar kar rahay hain
5,64,"yahodi kehte hain Allah ke haath bandhay hue hain bandhay gay un ke haath, aur laanat pari inn par uss bakwaas ki badolat jo yeh karte hain Allah ke haath to kushadah hain, jis terhan chahta hai kharch karta hai haqeeqat yeh hai ke jo kalaam tumahray rab ki taraf se tum par nazil howa hai woh un mein se aksar logon ki sar kashi o baatil parasti mein ultay izafah ka mojab ban gaya hai, aur ( is ki Padaash mein ) hum ne un ke darmain qayamat taq ke liye adawat aur dushmani daal di hai jab kabhi yeh jung ki aag bhrhkate hain Allah uss ko thanda kar deta hai yeh zameen mein fasaad phelanay ki sae kar rahay hain magar Allah fasaad barpaa karne walon ko hargiz pasand nahi karta"
